        "TileImage": "$($repository 332280ad-3b31-4913-99f1-794a4a46b98b).Image",
        "Description": "An actress named Anaya Vinkuri has auditioned for a Hollywood film, but at her audition, was outshone by Haasan. Furthermore, Vinkuri and another actor, Gilford Bootyswang (stage name Gregory Arthur), have a long standing rivalry, and Bootyswang auditioned for the lead actor in the same film which Vinkuri auditioned. Vinkuri has hired you to eliminate both targets, to secure her part in the film, and to make sure she does not have to costar with Bootyswang. I will leave you to prepare, 47.",
